results.description: This was an interesting plant that I missed uploading at the coast. This was a really cool one. I don't always get to the coast all that often but every time I go I am always finding something new. This one was pretty purple flower with folded leaves. I have not really paid much attention to the flowers on a beach. Next time I go I need to photograph more of them.
